。。<br />\n<br />\n總商會主席葛理福（Robert Grieves）表示：「。。。。。。。。。。。。。」<br />\n<br />\n金融服務顧問公司Quinlan &amp; Associates行政總裁Benjamin Quinlan亦向《華爾街日報》表示，若未經本港立法機關而強推法例，將大大損害法治和削弱。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200524/large/1590252041_0564.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200524%2Flarge%2F1590252041_0564.gif&h=6b4542ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n哈西特<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n商界憂中共推報復措施<br />\n<br />\n美國會否因國安法改變香港的經貿地位，北京會否推報復措施令外企遭殃，是商界另一大憂慮。《紐時》和《華爾街日報》。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n《華盛頓郵報》昨社論指取消香港特殊地位將重創香港經濟，駐港美企亦受波及，將加速。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n對於國際社會紛紛反對，外交部駐港公署表示堅持反對外國妄加評論，憤言「一些國家一。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社/美國《華爾街日報》/《紐約時報》"},{"pid":"e3e588a46f39372e2b6033f5cabeea5d91f8a7dd","tid":2032159,"uid":213877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T02:01:31.000Z","msg":"快！！不要說了"},{"pid":"6b533320b8f15253f209bffa11b692c6b59c0ee1","tid":2032159,"uid":13724,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T02:03:22.000Z","msg":"同啲國企做生意，一得罪人就屈你意圖盗取國家機密癲覆政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b4a1c9d39873b6ac5cc3bf0ef0e65371f670143","tid":2032159,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T02:04:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Bkp2izngjf0/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FBkp2izngjf0%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=7811405a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/eBMyqmwQSs0/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FeBMyqmwQSs0%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=d4bb8c6a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e41580b0fac5515cac71906be5bd64c5a09e6c05","tid":2032159,"uid":282930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0